The paper deals with the intersection of computer vision and natural language processing, specifically in the context of captioned images. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are the most likely categories. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Learning) as possible categories. Finally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques, which suggests cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as a possible category.
